# Grid Backup Configuration
# DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE WITH SECRETS

# The restic repository location. 
# Examples:
#   Local: /opt/grid-vault
#   SFTP:  sftp:user@synology-ip:/volume1/grid-backups
